1) What is a port?
Ports are virtual places within an operating system where network connections start and end.

Windows -- RDP
LINUX -- SSH (Secure shell)

2) Mandatory information to connect with ec2?
1- UserName
2- DNS Or IP address
3- pem file or ppk file

3) When machines are in the same network then we use private ip and in different network we use public ip.



